This category lists, primarily, [[WP:Notability|notable]] [[United States nationality law|citizens of the United States]], in appropriate [[WP:Subcategory|sub-categories]]. Notable individuals who have otherwise lived in the United States are also sub-categorised, however, under [[:Category:Immigrants to the United States]], [[:Category:Expatriates in the United States]] or [[:Category:Ambassadors to the United States]].
